text: "Don't Make Me Over" is a 1962 popular ballad. It was written by Burt Bacharach and Hal David. Dionne Warwick sang this song. The song reached #5 on the Billboard R&B; charts. The song was later recorded by other artists, such as Jennifer Warnes and Julia Holter. ==References== Category:Pop songs Category:1962 songs Category:Dionne Warwick songs Category:Jennifer Warnes songs
title: Don't Make Me Over
